<main role="main" class="container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the Investment Club. We are dedicated to empowering our members through insightful investment opportunities and financial education. Our club, based in Uganda, focuses on building a community where investors can grow together. With a keen eye on the local market trends, we offer a platform for sharing strategies, resources, and experiences.</p>
    <p>Since our inception in 2021, we have grown to over 10 active members and manage a diversified portfolio including unit trusts, bonds, and real estate investments. Our approach is grounded in collaborative decision-making, transparency, and ethical investment practices. We believe in the strength of unity in investment to achieve financial independence.</p>
    <p>Join us to start your journey towards savvy investing and financial growth.</p>
</main>

